item.title: CVE-2024-32602|2024-04-18T10:25:58.111Z -- OnTheGoSystems -- WooCommerce Multilingual & Multicurrency
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection') vulnerability in OnTheGoSystems WooCommerce Multilingual & Multicurrency.This issue affects WooCommerce Multilingual & Multicurrency: from n/a through 5.3.3.1.
